description: [``botocore``] SDK and documentation updates for GetTemplateSummary API (unrecognized resources)

[``botocore``] Amazon Managed Grafana now supports grafanaVersion update for existing workspaces with UpdateWorkspaceConfiguration API. DescribeWorkspaceConfiguration API additionally returns grafanaVersion. A new ListVersions API lists available versions or, if given a workspaceId, the versions it can upgrade to.
[``botocore``] General Availability (GA) release of AWS Health Imaging, enabling customers to store, transform, and analyze medical imaging data at petabyte-scale.
[``botocore``] This release adds support for securely sharing with AWS service principals.
[``botocore``] Added support for SAP Hana High Availability discovery (primary and secondary nodes) and Backint agent installation with SSM for SAP.
[``botocore``] Added the URI path to the custom aggregation keys that you can specify for a rate-based rule.
